        public Node getOtherEntrance(Node entrance)
        Returns the other entrance of the portal
        Parameters:
        entrance - an entrance of the portal
        Returns:
        If entrance is a valid entry point to the portal, the other entrance is returned. Else a node with the position [-1, -1] is returned
